_sText:
This is the fifth of my texture map =)
I worked some weeks on that map and i have to say it's my best.
Much detail with "env_cubemap"'s and enough cover to hide.

Some grenades are waiting for ya at the top of the mid-tower but attention on your way to the top you dont have any cover.

Bot Nav File are included in the WinRar folder.

I hope you enjoy and have fun with my map =)

You can use my map for GunGame, Deathmatch and normal CSS ;)

It's realy fun to play my map with bots =) but the best way is to load the map on your Internet server and play it with your friends ;)

P.S: The 3dskybox is the first i have ever made so sry for nothing special in it.
P.P.S: Hope you understand my English lol
